%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20homeless%20Iowa%20mom%20of%202%20is%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20landlord%20who%20will%20accept%20her%20housing%20voucher%20before%20it%20expires.%20The%20state%20is%20making%20it%20harder%20by%20allowing%20landlords%20to%20discriminate%20against%20her.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20shows%20homes%20in%20Jesup%2C%20Iowa.%20Republican%20presidential%20candidates%20are%20currently%20criss-crossing%20Iowa%20as%20the%20states%20January%2015%20Republican%20caucus%20draws%20near.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f8c96a961b37edf3969a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20shows%20homes%20on%20December%2020%2C%202023%20in%20Jesup%2C%20Iowa.%20In%202021%2C%20Iowa%20passed%20a%20law%20barring%20cities%20and%20counties%20from%20protecting%20voucher%20holders%20from%20overt%20discrimination%20by%20landlords.%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStephanie%20Quinn%20was%20forced%20to%20move%20out%20of%20her%20Farley%2C%20Iowa%2C%20apartment%20this%20spring.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EQuinn's%20Section%208%20voucher%20and%20her%20children's%20schooling%20hinge%20on%20finding%20new%20housing%20by%20July%2011.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIowa%20law%20allows%20landlords%20to%20refuse%20vouchers%2C%20complicating%20Quinn's%20search%20for%20a%20new%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Quinn%20was%20at%20work%20when%20her%20kids%2C%2010%20and%2012%2C%20received%20a%20paper%20notice%20from%20their%20landlord%20informing%20them%20that%20the%20family%20wouldn't%20be%20offered%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20their%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Farley%2C%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2043-year-old%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20Quinn%20had%2030%20days%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20place%20she%20and%20her%20kids%20had%20called%20home%20for%20five%20years.%20The%20family%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20nearly%20two%20months%20staying%20with%20Quinn's%20boyfriend%20in%20his%20one-bedroom%20apartment%2C%20so%20that%20the%20kids%20can%20finish%20out%20their%20school%20year.%20But%20the%20living%20arrangement%20isn't%20sustainable%2C%20and%20Quinn%20has%20a%20looming%20deadline%20to%20find%20a%20new%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20deadline%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0July%2011%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20imposed%20by%20the%20state%20housing%20authority%20and%20applies%20to%20Quinn's%20Section%208%20housing%20choice%20voucher%2C%20which%20she's%20had%20for%20about%2012%20years.%20Quinn%20suffers%20from%20Charcot-Marie-Tooth%20disease%2C%20which%20affects%20her%20motor%20and%20sensory%20nerves%2C%20compromising%20her%20mobility%20in%20her%20arms%20and%20legs.%20Though%20she%20receives%20about%20%241%2C000%20per%20month%20in%20social%20security%20disability%20insurance%2C%20she%20also%20works%20at%20a%20local%20Subway%20sandwich%20shop%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Quinn%20doesn't%20find%20a%20new%20apartment%20with%20a%20landlord%20who%20will%20accept%20her%20voucher%20before%20July%2011%2C%20she'll%20lose%20the%20crucial%20housing%20benefit%2C%20according%20to%20paperwork%20she%20received%20from%20the%20housing%20authority%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed.%20With%20the%20voucher%2C%20Quinn%20paid%20up%20to%20about%20%24250%20of%20her%20%24875%20rent%20each%20month%2C%20as%20the%20program%20requires%20tenants%20to%20spend%20no%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20their%20income%20on%20rent.%20If%20she%20loses%20her%20voucher%2C%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iowalegalaid.org%2Fresource%2Fwaiting-lists-and-public-housing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elikely%20take%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20have%20to%20go%20back%20on%20waiting%20lists%2C%20and%20I'm%20actually%20on%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20other%20waiting%20lists%20for%20income-based%20places%2C%20too%2C%20and%20they're%20about%20five%20years%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Quinn%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22714e5540-26a0-4866-9b30-350de38d17fd%5C%22%3EIowa%20lets%20landlords%20refuse%20voucher%20holders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20says%20she's%20contacted%20close%20to%2030%20landlords%20since%20March.%20Many%20have%20simply%20told%20her%20they%20don't%20accept%20housing%20vouchers.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstateline.org%2F2023%2F07%2F21%2Fsome-states-protect-section-8-renters-but-enforcement-is-elusive%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E17%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20an%20applicant%20down%20solely%20because%20they%20have%20a%20voucher%20is%20illegal%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20practice%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hud.gov%2Fprogram_offices%2Fpublic_indian_housing%2Fprograms%2Fhcv%2Fsource-of-income-protections%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esource-of-income%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Iowa%2C%20the%20practice%20is%20allowed.%20In%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2021%2F5%2F5%2F22417878%2Fiowa-kim-reynolds-section-8-housing-vouchers-renters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20state%20passed%20a%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20barring%20cities%20and%20counties%20from%20protecting%20voucher%20holders%20from%20overt%20discrimination%20by%20landlords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20received%20a%20list%20of%20apartment%20options%20from%20the%20local%20housing%20authority%2C%20but%20the%20listings%20are%20mostly%20outdated.%20So%20she's%20turned%20to%20looking%20for%20rental%20listings%20on%20Zillow%2C%20Trulia%2C%20and%20even%20Facebook%20and%20Craigslist.%20But%20when%20she's%20inquired%20with%20these%20landlords%20and%20informed%20them%20that%20she%20has%20a%20voucher%2C%20they've%20largely%20rejected%20her%20outright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20complete%20'no'%20right%20away%20and%20'no%20we%20don't%20do%20that%2C%20no%20we%20don't%20accept%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20wasn't%20on%20the%20housing%20list%2C%20I%20pretty%20much%20got%20a%20no.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20has%20found%20a%20few%20property%20owners%20who%20say%20they'll%20take%20her%20voucher%2C%20but%20they're%20almost%20an%20hour%20away%20from%20Farley%20and%20Quinn%20needs%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20area%20to%20keep%20her%20kids%20enrolled%20in%20their%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20school%20lets%20out%20for%20summer%20break%2C%20Quinn's%20kids%20will%20move%20in%20with%20a%20close%20friend%20in%20Dubuque%20until%20Quinn%20can%20find%20a%20new%20apartment.%20If%20she%20doesn't%20find%20a%20new%20home%20in%20the%20area%20before%20July%2C%20she's%20worried%20she'll%20have%20to%20temporarily%20put%20her%20kids%20in%20foster%20care%20so%20they%20can%20continue%20attending%20their%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20is%20also%20concerned%20she%20won't%20live%20close%20enough%20to%20her%2083-year-old%20grandmother%2C%20who%20she's%20the%20sole%20caretaker%20for.%20And%20she%20fears%20having%20to%20give%20up%20her%20job.%20The%20managers%20at%20her%20Subway%20shop%20have%20been%20very%20accommodating%20of%20her%20needs%2C%20purchasing%20special%20knives%20she%20can%20use%20and%20exempting%20her%20from%20finding%20replacements%20to%20take%20her%20shift%20when%20she's%20out%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20upset%20that%20if%20I%20can't%20find%20something%20nearby%2C%20I%20have%20to%20leave%20this%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248907474-9394-46ff-857b-c63d67223959%5C%22%3EA%20crucial%20but%20flawed%20benefit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20Housing%20Choice%20Voucher%20Program%20is%20the%20biggest%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20most%20effective%20%E2%80%94%20American%20housing%20assistance%20program.%20It%20aids%20about%205%20million%20people%20in%202.3%20million%20households%20who%20make%20less%20than%2050%25%20of%20their%20area%20median%20income%20to%20find%20rental%20housing%20on%20the%20private%20market.%20But%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huduser.gov%2Fportal%2Fpdredge%2Fpdr-edge-featd-article-051623.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclining%20number%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20landlords%20across%20the%20US%20are%20accepting%20the%20vouchers%2C%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20recipients%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huduser.gov%2Fpublications%2Fpdf%2Fsec8success.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efailing%20to%20secure%20housing%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20program%2C%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-vouchers-crisis-funding-landlords-restrictions-inspections-renters-struggle-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20program%20is%20severely%20underfunded.%20Quinn%20is%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbpp.org%2Fresearch%2Fhousing%2Fpolicy-basics-project-based-vouchers%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOnly%25201%2520in%25204%2520families%2Cof%2520families%2520eligible%2520for%2520vouchers.%26amp%3Btext%3DAgencies%2520can%2520maintain%2520separate%2520waitlists%2Csingle%2520waitlist%2520for%2520all%2520vouchers.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20in%20four%3C%2Fa%3E%20eligible%20Americans%20who%20actually%20receive%20a%20voucher.%20And%20the%20average%20wait%20time%20for%20recipients%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbpp.org%2Fresearch%2Fhousing%2Ffamilies-wait-years-for-housing-vouchers-due-to-inadequate-funding%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20and%20a%20half%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20About%2010%20million%20additional%20low-income%20households%20are%20going%20without%20the%20help%20they%20qualify%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Quinn%2C%20many%20voucher%20holders%20struggle%20to%20find%20a%20home%20that%20meets%20the%20program's%20requirements%20and%20a%20landlord%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20applicant%20within%20the%20limited%20time%20%E2%80%94%20as%20short%20as%2060%20days%20%E2%80%94%20allotted%20to%20find%20a%20unit.%20Nationwide%2C%20only%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huduser.gov%2Fportal%2Fportal%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2FVoucher-Success_Rates.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E60%25%20of%20voucher%20recipients%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20successful%20in%20finding%20a%20home%20with%20the%20subsidy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHousing%20experts%20have%20found%20that%20the%20home%20inspection%20process%20is%20a%20major%20pain%20point%20in%20the%20program.%20Before%20a%20voucher%20recipient%20can%20sign%20a%20lease%20on%20a%20home%2C%20it%20must%20be%20inspected%20by%20the%20local%20housing%20authority%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20meets%20a%20slew%20of%20health%20and%20safety%20standards.%20But%20that%20process%20can%20create%20lengthy%20delays%2C%20cause%20landlords%20to%20keep%20a%20unit%20empty%20and%20miss%20out%20on%20rent%20payments%2C%20and%20ultimately%20result%20in%20the%20voucher%20holder%20losing%20out%20on%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20a%20voucher%20recipient%20can%20even%20get%20to%20the%20inspection%20process%2C%20they%20need%20to%20find%20a%20suitable%20home%20that%20will%20take%20a%20voucher.%20Many%20landlords%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urban.org%2Fresearch%2Fpublication%2Fpilot-study-landlord-acceptance-housing-choice-vouchers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereject%20voucher%20holders%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20in%20places%20where%20source-of-income%20discrimination%20is%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deck%20is%20even%20more%20stacked%20against%20low-income%20people%20in%20a%20state%20like%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20hopes%20her%20story%20will%20help%20others%20in%20even%20worse%20situations.%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20a%20good%20family%20support%20system%2C%20and%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20have%20that%2C%26quot%3B%