ionals%20after%20they%20were%20allegedly%20hit%20by%20a%20Porsche%20in%20Pune%20has%20once%20again%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20India's%20hit-and-run%20scourge.%20And%20data%C2%A0paint%C2%A0a%20grim%20picture.%20The%20rise%20in%20such%20accidents%2C%20involving%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%2C%20and%20motorcyclists%2C%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20concern%20among%20authorities%20and%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20it%20is%20making%20news%20at%20the%20moment%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20Pune%20Porsche%20case%20has%20reignited%20the%20concern%20surrounding%20hit-and-run%20accidents%20in%20India.%20In%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20May%2019%2C%20two%20young%20IT%20professionals%20lost%20their%20lives%20when%20their%20motorcycle%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20Taycan%2C%20allegedly%20driven%20at%20150%C2%A0kmph%C2%A0by%20a%2017-year%20old.%20Reports%20suggested%20that%20the%20teenager%20behind%20the%20wheel%20was%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20collision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EDeaths%20by%20road%20accidents%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%20alone%2C%20there%20were%201%2C48%2C716%20reported%20incidents%20of%20deaths%20due%20to%20negligence%20in%20road%20accidents.%20The%20crime%20rate%20registered%20at%20a%20concerning%2011.1%20per%20lakh%20population%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Crime%20in%20India%20Report%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EHit-and-run%20cases%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHit-and-run%20cases%20accounted%20for%2046%2C907%20reported%20accidents%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%2049%2C893%20lives%2C%20with%20a%20crime%20rate%20of%203.5%20per%20lakh%20population%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20With%2017%2C296%20deaths%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20witnessed%20the%20most%20hit-and-run%20deaths%20in%202022%2C%20followed%20by%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%20with%209073%20and%203632%20deaths%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20adults%20aged%2018-45%20years%20bore%20the%