industrial%20profits%20rise%2C%20likely%20intensifying%20trade%20tensions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20countries%20are%20lining%20up%20to%20call%20out%20China%20for%20its%20barrage%20of%20cheap%20exports%20that%20are%20flooding%20the%20world's%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20criticism%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-flood-solar-panel-cell-market-garden-fence-overcapacity-yellen-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen%3C%2Fa%3E%20broaching%20the%20issue%20last%20month%20during%20her%20trip%20to%20China.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20Europe's%20top%20economy%20echoed%20the%20same%20concerns%20when%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20visited%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20weekend%2C%20France%20%E2%80%94%20the%20European%20Union's%20second-largest%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20economic%20model%20in%20which%20China%20is%20producing%20more%20and%20more%20cheaper%20industrial%20devices%20because%20it%20could%20be%20a%20threat%20not%20only%20for%20the%20EU%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20US%2C%20but%20for%20the%20global%20world%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20finance%20minister%20Bruno%20Le%20Maire%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-05-26%2Fchina-s-industry-threatens-entire-global-economy-france-warns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20TV.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20address%20that%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELe%20Maire's%20complaint%20came%20after%20finance%20chiefs%20from%20the%20Group%20of%20Seven%2C%20or%20G7%2C%20stepped%20up%20their%20game%20with%20a%20sharp%20rebuke%20to%20China%20following%20a%20meeting%20in%20the%20resort%20town%20of%20Stresa%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20reaffirming%20our%20interest%20in%20a%20balanced%20and%20reciprocal%20collaboration%2C%20we%20express%20concerns%20about%20China's%20comprehensive%20use%20of%20non-market%20policies%20and%20practices%20that%20undermines%20our%20workers%2C%20industries%2C%20and%20economic%20resilience%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g7italy.it%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FStresa-Communique-25-May-2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EG7%20finance%20ministers%20and%20central%20bank%20governors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20the%20potential%20negative%20impacts%20of%20overcapacity%20and%20will%20consider%20taking%20steps%20to%20ensure%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20in%20line%20with%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20(WTO)%20principles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f4415ba-2ca7-4435-8934-c08ccdff665f%5C%22%3EChina%20pushes%20back%20on%20criticism%2C%20industrial%20profits%20rose%20in%20April%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20consistently%20resisted%20the%20West's%20criticism%20that%20it%20is%20dumping%20cheap%20goods%20on%20the%20world%20market.%20Chinese%20authorities%20say%20the%20West's%20accusations%20are%20protectionist%20and%20aimed%20at%20containing%20China's%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20cannot%20be%20labeled%20'overcapacity'%20simply%20because%20a%20country's%20production%20capacity%20exceeds%20its%20domestic%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20He%20Yadong%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.news.cn%2F20240516%2F280e8b8ed85d4a20a03dbc8593a888fc%2Fc.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20Commerce%20Ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20many%20developed%20nations%20have%20been%20exporting%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20goods%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20should%20not%20criticize%20China%20for%20exporting%20too%20many%20new%20energy%20products%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20West%20is%20taking%20aim%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20producing%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20energy%20products%20as%20the%20country%20navigates%20a%20painful%20economic%20transition%2C%20from%20one%20reliant%20on%20real%20estate%20and%20low-cost%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20hot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-new-growth-areas-electric-vehicles-batteries-solar-property-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bnew%20three%26quot%3B%20sectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20lithium%20batteries%2C%20and%20solar%20panels.%20The%20West%20is%20also%20eyeing%20those%20fast-rising%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20profits%20at%20China's%20industrial%20companies%20rose%204%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20reversing%20a%20drop%20in%20March%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stats.gov.cn%2Fsj%2Fzxfb%2F202405%2Ft20240527_1956067.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficial%20statistics%20released%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20profits%20also%20rose%20about%204%25%20in%20the%20first%20four%20months%20of%20the%20year%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%2076%25%20surge%20in%20the%20earnings%20of%20computer%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20other%20electric%20equipment%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%20In%20comparison%2C%20profits%20at%20general%20equipment%20manufacturers%20rose%20just%206%25%20from%20January%20to%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20profits%20at%20industrial%20enterprises%20recovered%20steadily%20from%20January%20to%20April%2C%20%26quot%3Bdomestic%20demand%20remains%20insufficient%2C%20and%20the%20external%20demand%20environment%20remains%20complex%20and%20severe%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stats.gov.cn%2Fsj%2Fsjjd%2F202405%2Ft20240527_1956068.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYu%20Weining%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20government%20statistician%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20data%20from%20China%20is%20likely%20to%20add%20even%20more%20tensions%20to%20the%20trade%20tiff%20between%20Beijing%20and%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255e8d6f6-917b-4e7c-9cbd-38761f1ca0b1%5C%22%3EAvoiding%20'China%20shock'%202.0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F05%2F14%2Ffact-sheet-president-biden-takes-action-to-protect-american-workers-and-businesses-from-chinas-unfair-trade-practices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20unveiled%20sharply%20higher%20tariffs%20on%20a%20range%20of%20imports%20from%20China%2C%20including%20electric%20vehicle%20batteries%20and%20semiconductor%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Fip_23_4752%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EEuropean%20Commission%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20an%20ongoing%20probe%20into%20whether%20EV%20imports%20from%20China%20benefited%20from%20illegal%20subsidization%20that%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20threatens%20to%20damage%20the%20EU's%20EV%20manufacturers.%20If%20this%20is%20found%20to%20be%20true%2C%20the%20EU%20could%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20these%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West's%20hawkish%20moves%20toward%20China%20now%20follow%20the%20East%20Asian%20giant's%20breakneck%20industrialization%20to%20its%20position%20as%20the%20factory%20of%20the%20world%20over%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%20That%20quick%20ascendance%20wiped%20out%20jobs%20and%20decimated%20communities%20elsewhere%20%E2%80%94%20a%20phenomenon%20three%20researchers%20termed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-shock-explainer-us-economy-trade-dumping-supply-glut-yellen-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BChina%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20West%20wants%20