g%2075%2C000%20points.%20Mobius%20was%20questioned%20about%20his%20earlier%20prediction%20of%20the%20Sensex%20hitting%20the%20one%20lakh%20mark%2C%20here's%20what%20he%20had%20to%20say%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fwhen-will-bse-sensex-hit-1-lakh-mark-mobius-says-indian-markets-will%2Farticleshow%2F110456966.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhen%20Big%20Cars%20Hit...%26quot%3B%3A%20Noida%20Family%20Waits%20For%20Justice%20In%20Audi%20Hit-And-Run%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20the%2063-year-old%20man%2C%20who%20died%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20speeding%20Audi%20in%20Noida's%20Sector%2053%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20going%20slow%20in%20its%20investigation%20and%20said%20it%20is%20the%20family%20which%20arranged%20the%20chilling%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanak%20Dev%20Shah%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20speeding%20luxury%20car%20yesterday%20when%20he%20had%20stepped%20out%20to%20get%20milk%20from%20the%20nearby%20depot.%20His%20son%20Sandip%20told%20NDTV%20that%20he%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20accident%20around%206%20am.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20leaving%20for%20a%20walk%20when%20my%20neighbour%20came%20and%20told%20me%20that%20my%20father%20had%20an%20accident.%20I%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot.%20By%20then%2C%20a%20PCR%20van%20had%20taken%20my%20father%20to%20the%20hospital.%20We%20went%20to%20Manas%20Hospital%20in%20Sector%2034.%20And%20we%20were%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Shah%20said%20that%20when%20they%20went%20to%20the%20cops%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%2C%20they%20were%20told%20to%20get%20the%20autopsy%20done%20first.%20%26quot%3BThe%20FIR%20was%20registered%20when%20the%20autopsy%20report%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fopqv5m98_noida-hit-and-run_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20Mishra%2C%20Additional%20DCP%2C%20Noida%20Police%2C%20has%20said%20police%20are%20scanning%20the%20CCTV%20footage.%20The%20car%20and%20its%20driver%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20traced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20cops%20arranged%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20that%20captures%20the%20luxury%20car%20hitting%20the%20elderly%20man%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20we%20arranged%20it%20ourselves.%20We%20got%20no%20support%20from%20the%20police%20and%20the%20administration.%20If%20they%20backed%20us%2C%20the%20culprit%20would%20have%20been%20arrested%20by%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lost%20the%20head%20of%20our%20family%2C%20so%20you%20can%20understand%20what%20is%20our%20mental%20condition%20now.%20The%20administration%20should%20help%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20said%20his%20father%20used%20to%20work%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Radio%20and%20had%20retired%20three%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20neighbour%20alleged%20that%20when%20the%20family%20reached%20the%20local%20police%20station%20and%20asked%20for%20an%20update%20on%20the%20case%2C%20a%20cop%20replied%20that%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%20your%20case%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20We%20are%20pushing%20them%20to%20probe%20different%20angles.%20Are%20we%20the%20police%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20big%20cars%20hit%20people%2C%20no%20action%20is%20taken.%20If%20it%20was%20a%20common%20man%2C%20he%20would%20be%20picked%20up.%20We%20are%20showing%20them%20it%20is%20an%20Audi%2C%20they%20are%20insisting%20on%20referring%20to%20it%20as%20a%20'white%20car'.%20Every%20person%20has%20a%20right%20to%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20neighbours%20are%20with%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20said%20that%20Mr%20Shah%20would%20to%20the%20nearby%20Mother%20Dairy%20depot%20to%20get%20milk%20every%20morning.%20Sometimes%2C%20he%20would%20also%20take%20his%20grandson%20along.%20But%20on%20Sunday%2C%20he%20went%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGita%20Vaishnav%2C%20Mr%20Shah's%20neighbour%20and%20an%20eyewitness%2C%20said%20the%20elderly%20man%20greeted%20her%20that%20morning%2C%20minutes%20before%20the%20accident.%20%26quot%3BThe%20car%20was%20moving%20in%20a%20zigzag%20manner.%20Before%20I%20could%20alert%20him%2C%20the%20car%20hit%20him.%20He%20was%20thrown%2010%20feet%20in%20the%20air%2C%20he%20hit%20the%20car%20and%20then%20fell%20on%20the%20ground%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Noida%20hit-and-run%20horror%20comes%20shortly%20after%20the%20Pune%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20a%2017-year-old's%20late-night%20dash%20in%20a%20Porsche%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20dead.%20The%20incidents%20have%20sparked%20a%20conversation%20on%20how%20road%20safety%20rules%20are%20being%20flouted%20and%20how%20power%20and%20influence%20being%20used%20to%20shield%20the%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Noida%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20two%20people%20were%20killed%20after%20a%20BMW%20with%20a%20minor%20behind%20the%20wheel%20hit%20an%20e-rickshaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20of%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20on%20accidental%20deaths%20and%20suicides%20in%20India%2C%20a%20total%20of%204%2C46%2C768%20road%20accidents%20were%20reported%20in%202022.%20These%20left%201%2C71%2C100%20deaths%20and%20over%204.23%20lakh%20people%20injured.%20About%2062%20per%20cent%20of%20these%20accidents%20were%20caused%20due%20to%20overspeeding%20and%20claimed%20over%201%20lakh%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17167930800