%20by%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%202000%20rules%2C%20which%20were%20again%20amended%20in%202006%20and%202010.%20This%20was%20replaced%20by%20the%20current%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202015.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-cash-kidnapping-how-pune-teens-family-tried-to-shift-blame-after-crash-5742076%5C%22%3EThe%20dreadful%20incident%20in%20Pune%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-if-you-talk-what-porsche-teens-grandfather-told-driver-after-crash-5741599%5C%22%3Eclaimed%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20young%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-teens-father-charged-with-cheating-jailed-till-june-7-5736465%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20due%20to%20drunken%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-pune-teen-drunk-fought-with-driver-to-drive-porsche-which-led-to-crash-sources-5734104%5C%22%3Erash%20driving%20by%20a%20juvenile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20posed%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20functional%20efficiency%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20current%20laws%2C%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Act%20in%20particular.%20The%20Section%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20distinctly%20categorised%20juveniles%20between%2016%20and%2018%20years%20of%20age%20involved%20in%20heinous%20offences.%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20deviation%20from%20the%20previous%20rules%2C%20which%20treated%20all%20juveniles%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Pune%20incident%2C%20the%20act%20of%20granting%20bail%20to%20the%20juvenile%20on%20trivial%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20writing%20an%20essay%20on%20traffic%20safety%20and%20assisting%20the%20traffic%20police%2C%20was%20not%20only%20naive%20but%20also%20patently%20illegal.%20It%20was%2C%20however%2C%20sought%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bcorrected%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20subsequent%20decision%20to%20send%20the%20juvenile%20to%20a%20remand%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJumbled%20Processes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2015%20of%20the%20Act%20is%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Bpreliminary%20assessment%20into%20heinous%20offences%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bmental%20and%20physical%20capacity%20(of%20the%20juvenile)%20to%20commit%20such%20offence%2C%20ability%20to%20understand%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20offence%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20alleged%20offence.%20The%20assistance%20of%20experts%20can%20be%20availed%20for%20this%20purpose.%20Based%20on%20this%20assessment%2C%20invoking%20Section%2018(3)%20of%20the%20Act%20by%20deciding%20that%20the%20child%20should%20be%20tried%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20the%20Board%20can%20transfer%20the%20case%20to%20a%20children's%20court%20for%20trial.%20The%20children's%20court%20can%20again%20re-examine%20this%20decision.%20Even%20after%20the%20trial%2C%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20death%20penalty%20or%20life%20imprisonment%20is%20impermissible%20on%20account%20of%20the%20embargo%20under%20Section%2021%20of%20the%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20procedures%20are%20neither%20simple%20nor%20easy.%20The%20Boards%20are%20often%20clueless%20regarding%20the%20exact%20parameters%20for%20trying%20a%20child%20as%20an%20adult.%20In%3Cem%3E%20Barun%20Chandra%20Thakur%20v.%20Master%20Bholu%20And%20Another%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2022)%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20comprehensively%20dealt%20with%20the%20deficits%20in%20the%20provisions%20and%20directed%20that%20guidelines%20be%20formulated.%20It%20interpreted%20the%20proviso%20to%20Section%2015%20to%20mean%20that%20the%20Board%20shall%20take%20the%20assistance%20of%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20psychologists%20or%20psycho-social%20workers%20or%20other%20experts%26quot%3B.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bexpedient%20that%20appropriate%20and%20specific%20guidelines%20in%20this%20regard%20are%20put%20in%20place%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Focus%20On%20Social%20Background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%20came%20out%20with%20regulations%20for%20facilitating%20the%20effective%20application%20of%20Section%2015.%20It%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20existing%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20Social%20Investigation%20Report%20(SIR)%20and%20Social%20Background%20Report%20(SBR)%20are%20exhaustive%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20assessments%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20individualistic.%20Therefore%2C%20according%20to%20the%20guideline%2C%20they%20are%20designed%20%26quot%3Bto%20include%20the%20essential%20components%20and%20basic%20mechanism%20involved%20in%20preliminary%20assessment%20to%20address%20the%20ambiguity%20in%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20process%20and%20steps%20to%20be%20followed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20set%20of%20guidelines%20reminded%20the%20authorities%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Baim%20of%20the%20preliminary%20assessment%20is%20not%20to%20seek%20confession%20from%20the%20child%20nor%20to%20reach%20a%20conclusion%20of%20any%20sort%26quot%3B.%20It%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20confessional%20statement%20from%20the%20Social%20Investigation%20Report%20(SIR)%20must%20not%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%20while%20conducting%20preliminary%20assessment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-doctors-arrested-for-manipulating-blood-test-report-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-say-sources-5753624%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Pune%20Teen's%20Blood%20Sample%20Was%20Thrown%20In%20Dustbin%2C%20Forensic%20Head%20Arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guidelines%20explained%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20social%20background%20report%2C%20depicting%20details%20of%20antecedents%20and%20the%20family%20background%20of%20the%20child%2C%20individual%20care%20plan%2C%20etc%2C%20should%20be%20prepared.%20More%20importantly%2C%20they%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20final%20report%20should%20not%20include%20any%20kind%20of%20statement%20or%20document%20that%20could%20be%20incriminating%20in%20nature%26quot%3B.%20The%20guidelines%20contain%20certain%20%26quot%3Bsuggestive%20questions%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20report%26quot%3B%20and%20hypothetical%20illustrations%2C%20as%20annexures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreach%20Is%20The%20Norm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20such%20efforts%2C%20things%20did%20not%20improve%20substantially%20on%20the%20ground.%20In%20a%20case%20reported%20as%20%3Cem%3EChild%20in%20Conflict%20with%20Law%20v.%20State%20of%20Gujarat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2023)%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20set%20aside%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20and%20directed%20it%20to%20conduct%20a%20fresh%20assessment%20based%20on%20the%20guidelines%20that%20the%20court%20explained%20in%20detail.%20In%20another%20judgment%2C%20%3Cem%3EMustafa%20Khan%20Jabbar%20Khan%20v.%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2023)%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20set%20aside%20the%20order%20by%20the%20children's%20court%20(sessions%20court)%20and%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20and%20enumerated%20the%20breaches%20of%20the%20statutory%20prescriptions%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20assessment.%20Ironically%2C%20breaches%20remain%20the%20norm%2C%20and%20due%20compliance%20with%20the%20provisions%2C%20exceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20highlights%20is%20that%20the%20complex%20nature%20of%20the%20issue%20should%20call%20for%20radical%20reform%20in%20terms%20of%20institutions%20and%20society's%20outlook.%20The%20persons%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20should%20be%20properly%20selected%20and%20trained%20adequately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-pizza-fake-viral-rap-rs-48-000-bill-pizza-before-alcohol-test-probe-widens-in-pune-porsche-crash-5733650%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%E2%82%B9%C2%A048%2C000%20Bill%2C%20Pizza%20Before%20Alcohol%20Test%3A%20Probe%20Widens%20In%20Pune%20Porsche%20Crash%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChapter%203%20of%20the%20guidelines%20by%20the%20NCPCR%20talks%20about%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20and%20other%20experts%2C%20but%20the%20NCPCR%20does%20not%20call%20for%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20ad-hocism%20that's%20prevalent%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20appointment%20of%20experts.%20It%20foresees%20the%20situation%20where%20experts%20may%20not%20even%20be%20available%20in%20a%20district.%20In%20this%20author's%20view%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20permanent%20panel%20of%20experts%20at%20the%20state%20level%20to%20nip%20this%20ad-hocism.%20The%20lack%20of%20clarity%20in%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Boards%20over%20picking%20and%20choosing%20experts%20on%20a%20temporary%20basis%20for%20deciding%20the%20fate%20of%20juveniles%20or%20their%20family%20members%20is%20undesirable.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20a%20permanent%20panel%20and%20security%20of%20tenure%20for%20the%20experts%20so%20as%20to%20foster%20better%20responsibility.%20The%20legal%20aid%20system%20should%20also%20be%20revamped%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20parties%20are%20free%20to%20choose%20their%20lawyer%20and%20the%20state%20bears%20the%20expenses%20of%20such%20a%20lawyer%20-%20even%20if%20it's%20a%20bit%20costly.%20The%20current%20system%20of%20legal%20aid%20often%20does%20not%20provide%20for%20such%20things%20and%20imposes%20a%20set%20of%20empanelled%20lawyers%20on%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaw%20Can't%20Be%20A%20Panacea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20we%20need%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20text%20of%20the%20statutes%2C%20and%20even%20the%20judgments%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20realities%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20executive%20authorities%20and%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20child%20need%20to%20be%20made%20accountable%20when%20heinous%20offences%20are%20committed%20by%20juveniles.%20Sufficient%20methods%20for%20compensation%20should%20be%20evolved%20-%20though%20no%20amount%20of%20compensation%20would%20be%20sufficient%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20stark%20rise%20in%20India%20in%20heinous%20crimes%20committed%20by%20children%20aged%20between%2016%20and%2018%20years%20of%20age.%20Government%20data%20shows%C2%A0that%20as%20many%20as%20853%20murder%20and%201%2C688%20rape%20cases%20were%20registered%20against%20juveniles%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plethora%20of%20factors%20like%20bad%20parenting%2C%20illiteracy%2C%20poverty%2C%20as%20well%20as%20affluence%2C%20apart%20from%20family%20background%20and%20social%20conditions%2C%20have%20shaped%20juvenile%20crimes%20of%20our%20times.%20The%20law%20has%20its%20limitations%3B%20it%20is%20seldom%20a%20preventive%20device.%20The%20real%20solution%20should%20emerge%20from%20Indian%20households%20and%20schools%20as%20these%20are%20the%20places%20and%20the%20circumstances%20that%20shape%20children%2C%20even%20though%20they%20have%20very%20little%20or%20limited%20control%20over%20these%20environments.%20%26quot%3BA%20child%20is%20an%20uncut%20diamond%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20writer%20Austin%20O'Malley.%20Let%20us%20not%20think%20that%20the%20law%20is%20the%20only%20tool%20to%20shape%20this%20diamond.%20The%20tools%20are%20many%2C%20and%20they%20are%20often%20found%20beyond%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kaleeswaram%20Raj%20is%20a%20lawyer%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716793020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fti6q3gr8_pune-porsche-crash_625x300_24_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F