%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20my%20relatives%20are%20farmers%20and%20also%20grow%20plants%20at%20home.%20I%20asked%20them%20for%20gardening%20tips%20and%20started%20my%20journey%20%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETending%20to%20the%20money%20plant%20gave%20the%20gardener%20the%20confidence%20to%20try%20growing%20more%20plants.%20She%20ventured%20into%20growing%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20which%20she%20would%20feed%20her%20son%20daily.%20Later%2C%20she%20added%20more%20vegetables%2C%20such%20as%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%20and%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20growing%20vegetables%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20easy%2C%20she%20discovered%2C%20as%20she%20encountered%20many%20failures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20one%20harvest%20of%20tomatoes%20but%20the%20next%20one%20would%20fail.%20I%20referred%20to%20several%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20learn%20the%20ropes%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20experience%20is%20the%20biggest%20teacher.%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20when%20and%20how%20often%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20and%20give%20fertiliser.%20How%20much%20direct%20sunlight%20should%20be%20given%20was%20also%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20she%20learnt%20that%20it%20was%20ideal%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20early%20morning%2C%20between%207%20to%208%20am%2C%20the%20best%20time%20to%20do%20pest%20control%20was%20either%20before%206%20am%20or%20after%206%20pm%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20generally%20need%20more%20water.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20the%20needs%20of%20each%20vegetable%2C%20flower%20and%20fruit%20was%20different%2C%20and%20she%20would%20have%20to%20work%20her%20way%20around%20that%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGardening%20as%20therapy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20her%20plants%20started%20growing%20beautifully.%20Seeing%20her%20vegetables%20thrive%20gave%20her%20the%20confidence%20to%20start%20growing%20fruits.%20She%20also%20had%20a%20more%20important%20motive%20%E2%80%93%20encouraging%20her%20son%20to%20eat%20fruits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sushma%20(%40glitters.of.nature)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20guava%2C%20she%20today%20grows%20over%2070%20fruit%20trees%2C%20including%20mango%2C%20dragon%20fruit%2C%20custard%20apple%2C%20banana%2C%20papaya%2C%20strawberry.%20The%20trick%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20to%20buy%20grafted%20fruit%20plants%2C%20which%20will%20give%20you%20a%20better%20yield%20compared%20to%20seeds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20learnt%20this%20after%20she%20tried%20growing%20lemon%20and%2