0house.%20As%20my%20husband%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20much%2C%20I%20visited%20the%20collector%E2%80%99s%20office%20several%20times%20to%20prevent%20that.%20I%20visited%20the%20tehsildar%20and%20ran%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20save%20my%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dhanam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20mud%20house%20with%20a%20thatched%20roof%20is%20in%20dire%20straits.%20The%20walls%20are%20leaking%20and%20the%20house%20is%20filled%20with%20cobwebs.%20Rainy%20season%20is%20especially%20difficult%2C%20as%20even%20a%20small%20shower%20entails%20water%20coming%20inside%20the%20house.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20may%20fall%20down%20anytime.%20I%20request%20the%20government%20to%20help%20me%20build%20a%20new%20house.%20A%20small%20one%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20hardworking%20lady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337346%2Fdisability-inspiring-veena-ambarish-kari-dosa-food-cart-bengaluru-jp-nagar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20Dhanam%20Paati%20build%20a%20new%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20do%20so%20by%20donating%20to%20her%20account%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccount%20number%3A%20212086182%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBank%3A%20The%20Pudukkottai%20District%20Central%20Cooperative%20Bank%20Ltd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIFSC%20Code%3A%20TNSC0010900%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%3A%20Dhanam%20S%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Feature%20Image%20Courtesy%20M%20Muthu%20Kannan%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716298614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam1-1716293031.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350619%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20Dhanam%20paati%E2%80%99s%20idli%20shop%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20customers%20are%20